HEADWORD: Dal segno
<hw>Dal` se"gno</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[It., from the sign.]</ety>
<fld>(Mus.)</fld> <def>A direction to go back to the sign ⟦segno⟧ and
repeat from thence to the close. See <er>Segno</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

